articles.author: Maegan Vazquez,Allie Malloy
articles.title: Biden cancels visits to Australia and Papua New Guinea as debt ceiling negotiations continue - CNN
articles.description: President Joe Biden is canceling his upcoming visits to Papua New Guinea and Australia due to the ongoing debt ceiling negotiations in Washington, the White House confirmed Tuesday.
